強制便早點買食物，視乎強制多久，不能長期，我想二至三星期也可以，要有限期，沒理由無限期要求禁足。」<br />\n<br />\n李女士：「做得比較徹底些，帶動社會的人比較積極，人們便會安全，出入都好些。」<br />\n<br />\n李女士：「一定是(不方便)，問題是是否想疫情盡快過去，我覺得有時大家忍耐一下，長痛不如短痛。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，多五幢在油麻地佐敦指定區域的大廈，污水樣本持續呈陽性，須納入強制檢測範圍。<br />\n<br />\n在吳松街，早上有穿保護衣人員抽取污水樣本化驗，旁邊五棟大廈包括廟街漢興商業大廈、吳松街創遠樓、金源樓等，污水樣本持續呈陽性，大廈納入強制檢測範圍。當局要求任何人於本月8日起，曾經在大廈超過兩小時，星期日之前要接受病毒檢測。"},{"pid":"ef2d14b532f9ebe680f07567e21da731cbf52e12","tid":2375111,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:38:44.000Z","msg":"希望黎生唔係住或者返果頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9bd66b0f52ec37770c5b8397516e4fd64852d4","tid":2375111,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:39:44.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母...柒婆唔封關，驗完全港陰性都無用啦。"},{"pid":"a37d298db6e5ddbdd1135133f836eeb7a2c9ae4b","tid":2375111,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96398d0aaf4e5ea8e85d4e1b7fb454896e33dff","tid":2375111,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":85,"score":-82,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T19:36:05.000Z","msg":"香港人會反抗<br />\n無咁易做到<br />\n單係買餸就做唔到大陸咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"反條毛咩<br />\n啲防疫撚恐懼撚配合埋政府一齊捉尻人舉報人添啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"fd583b39a1fd91c2bf30f2d5b33fef296088b411","tid":2375111,"uid":5195,"like":246,"dislike":2,"score":244,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T19:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http